description: The AND of all the selectors represented by the `matchExpressions` selectors. This is currently only used in ResourceQuota.

matchExpressions.description: A list of scope selector requirements by `scope` of the resources. Note that the `"BestEffort"` and `"NotBestEffort"` scopes conflicts with each other, and the `"Terminating"` and the `"NotTerminating"` scopes conflict with each other.
